"name": "avg_npc_2101_1#4$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 18, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "所有人听着！", "name": "月见夜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2101_1#4$1"}, {"id": 19, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2101_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 20, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我犯了一个巨大的错误。", "name": "月见夜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2101_1#9$1"}, {"id": 21, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我将国家存亡，“试炼”的意义，“雷之主”的强大这些东西挂在嘴边，但归根结底，我想，我在恐惧面对它。", "name": "月见夜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2101_1#9$1"}, {"id": 22, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一旦对某件事产生了恐惧，人就会退缩，就会为自己找各种各样的借口进行逃避。", "name": "月见夜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2101_1#9$1"}, {"id": 23, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "建立狩猎团，将你们按照士兵的方式进行训练，阻止陛下前往挑战“雷之主”，并不是因为我有多么深谋远虑，而仅仅是因为——", "name": "月见夜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2101_1#9$1"}, {"id": 24, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2101_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 25, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我不够强大。", "name": "月见夜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2101_1#7$1"}, {"id": 26, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我甚至将这种恐惧传递给了你们。", "name": "月见夜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2101_1#7$1"}, {"id": 27, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我要求你们审慎，要求你们学会见机行事，要求你们不要为了狩猎拼上性命......", "name": "月见夜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2101_1#7$1"}, {"id": 28, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但是，我却没有把最重要的东西传达给你们。", "name": "月见夜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2101_1#7$1"}, {"id": 29, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2103_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 30, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唉，我说你啊，总是这么悲观又自大。", "name": "斑弥罗"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2103_1#1$1"}, {"id": 31, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "泡影国就算真的毁灭了，也不是你一个人的责任。", "name": "斑弥罗"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2103_1#1$1"}, {"id": 32, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2107_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 33, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "没错，将军，正如您平时告诫我们的那样，我们并非只是盲从您的命令而选择了保守。", "name": "随从武士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2107_1#1$1"}, {"id": 34, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我们选择成为狩猎团的一员，我们选择以成为武士的方式守卫我们的家园，是因为我们也认为，这样是正确的！", "name": "随从武士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2107_1#1$1"}, {"id": 35, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您从来没有做错过什么，如果我们真的失败了，那也只是我们做得不够好，仅此而已。", "name": "随从武士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2107_1#1$1"}, {"id": 36, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2101_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 37, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "月见夜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2101_1#2$1"}, {"id": 38, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2101_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 39, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "说的也是，或许比起后悔，我更应该庆幸。", "name": "月见夜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2101_1#5$1"}, {"id": 40, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "庆幸我最终得知了真相，庆幸我并没有成为想象中那个绝情的人。", "name": "月见夜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2101_1#5$1"}, {"id": 41, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "庆幸我此时此刻，至少还有能为陛下做到的事情。", "name": "月见夜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2101_1#5$1"}, {"id": 42, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2101_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 43, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "陛下。", "name": "月见夜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2101_1#7$1"}, {"id": 44, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我不断说服自己没有错，我不断告诉自己，我已经在诸多不好的选择中选择了相对正确的那一个。", "name": "月见夜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2101_1#7$1"}, {"id": 45, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2101_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 46, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "久而久之，它竟然似乎变成了唯一的答案......", "name": "月见夜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2101_1#9$1"}, {"id": 47, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我早该多和您聊一聊，我早该和您齐心协力。", "name": "月见夜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2101_1#9$1"}, {"id": 48, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2100_1#4$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 49, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "这一点，或许吾也是一样的。", "name": "宝巫迦"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2100_1#4$1"}, {"id": 50, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2100_1#3$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 51, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "回去之后，吾会和你开诚布公地聊一聊。", "name": "宝巫迦"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2100_1#3$1"}, {"id": 52, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2101_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 53, "prop": "multiline", "attributes": {"name": "月见夜", "content": "我期待着那天的到来。"}}, {"id": 54, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2101_1#4$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 55, "prop": "multiline", "attributes": {"name": "月见夜", "content": "狩猎团听令！"}}, {"id": 56, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 57, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_2106_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 58, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_2107_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 59, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在！", "name": "随从武士们"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2101_1#4$1"}, {"id": 60, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 61, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2101_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 62, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "以方阵为单位行动，向前推进，为宝巫迦陛下和“异兽猎人”开辟道路！", "name": "月见夜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2101_1#1$1"}, {"id": 63, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2101_1#4$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 64, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "为了我们的未来！", "name": "月见夜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2101_1#4$1"}, {"id": 65, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 66, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_2106_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 67, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_2107_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 68, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是！", "name": "随从武士们"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2101_1#4$1"}, {"id": 69, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 70, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 71, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 1.5, "xstrength": 70.0, "ystrength": 70.0, "vibrato": 70.0, "randomness": 95.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 72, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_sldrchrg", "volume": 1.0, "channel": "1"}}, {"id": 73, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "1", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 74, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 75, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "冲啊！为了泡影国，为了宝巫迦陛下！", "name": "随从武士们"}}, {"id": 76, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 77, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 78, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 2.0, "xstrength": 70.0, "ystrength": 70.0, "vibrato": 70.0, "randomness": 95.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 79, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_battlepresent", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 80, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 3.0}}, {"id": 81, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 82, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2103_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 83, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哈哈，我也来助你们一臂之力！", "name": "斑弥罗"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2103_1#1$1"}, {"id": 84, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 85, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_shipcannon"}}, {"id": 86, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 87, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_shipcannon"}}, {"id": 88, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 89, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 60.0, "ystrength": 60.0, "vibrato": 70.0, "randomness": 80.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 90, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_explosion"}}, {"id": 91, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 92, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 60.0, "ystrength": 60.0, "vibrato": 70.0, "randomness": 80.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 93, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_explosion"}}, {"id": 94, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 95, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 96, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2101_1#4$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 97, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "说真的，老朋友。", "name": "月见夜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2101_1#4$1"}, {"id": 98, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2101_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 99, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "世事当真是难以预料。", "name": "月见夜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2101_1#5$1"}, {"id": 100, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "想要做的事情总是一件也没有做好，结果，在以为自己即将失败的时候，却突然又发现，自己好像也没有那么失败。", "name": "月见夜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2101_1#5$1"}, {"id": 101, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2103_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 102, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "这你就不懂了，在我们发明界，这样的事情，几乎每天都要发生一次！", "name": "斑弥罗"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2103_1#1$1"}, {"id": 103, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "成功总是偶然的！但是，只要结果够好，不就可以了吗？", "name": "斑弥罗"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2103_1#1$1"}, {"id": 104, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2101_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 105, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哈，说的也是！", "name": "月见夜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2101_1#8$1"}, {"id": 106, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2101_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 107, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "陛下，去吧！", "name": "月见夜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2101_1#5$1"}, {"id": 108, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2103_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 109, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "陛下，要是需要火力支援就喊我，正好让我测试一下射程！", "name": "斑弥罗"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2103_1#1$1"}, {"id": 110, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2100_1#3$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 111, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯！", "name": "宝巫迦"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2100_1#3$1"}, {"id": 112, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 113, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 114, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 115, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 116, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 117, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 118, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 119, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 120, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "71_g11_invertedaltar_closed", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 121, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 122, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 123, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 124, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2100_1#1$1", "afrom": 0.0, "ato": 1.0, "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 125, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 126, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "这里......这座祭坛......过去的泡影国的人们就是在这里......", "name": "宝巫迦"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2100_1#1$1"}, {"id": 127, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2100_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 128, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "越是靠近这里，吾越是能清晰地感觉到“诅咒”的气息。", "name": "宝巫迦"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2100_1#8$1"}, {"id": 129, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2100_1#4$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 130, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "吾终于明白，在雪山时，那股牵引吾的力量究竟是什么了......", "name": "宝巫迦"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2100_1#4$1"}, {"id": 131, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "吾曾以为是“雷之主”，其实应该是“御轮”，一直以来，都是“御轮”在牵制吾......", "name": "宝巫迦"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2100_1#4$1"}, {"id": 132, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2100_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 133, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "母亲，一切的元凶，“试炼”的真相，是“御轮”，对吗？", "name": "宝巫迦"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2100_1#8$1"}, {"id": 134, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2100_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 135, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "吾来了，“雷之主”。", "name": "宝巫迦"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2100_1#9$1"}, {"id": 136, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 137, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 138, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 139, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 140, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 141, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "71_g11_invertedaltar_closed", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 142, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 143, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 144, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 145, "prop": "bgeffect", "attributes": {"name": "$eb_smock", "layer": 1.0}}, {"id": 146, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2102_1#1$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 147, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.5, "xstrength": 70.0, "ystrength": 70.0, "vibrato": 70.0, "randomness": 95.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 148, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$MHR_caxe_burst", "volume": 1.0, "channel": "burst1"}}, {"id": 149, "prop": "effect", "attributes": {"name": "$e_lighting", "layer": 1.0}}, {"id": 150, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 151, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.5, "xstrength": 70.0, "ystrength": 70.0, "vibrato": 70.0, "randomness": 95.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 152, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$MHR_caxe_burst", "volume": 1.0, "channel": "burst2"}}, {"id": 153, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 154, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.5, "xstrength": 70.0, "ystrength": 70.0, "vibrato": 70.0, "randomness": 95.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 155, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$MHR_caxe_burst", "volume": 1.0, "channel": "burst3"}}, {"id": 156, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 157, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$MHR_caxe_chainsaw_finish", "volume": 1.0, "channel": "finish"}}, {"id": 158, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 159, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 160, "prop": "bgeffect", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 161, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1048_orchd2_1#5$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 162, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "宝巫迦，趁现在！", "name": "梓兰"}, "figure_art": "avg_1048_orchd2_1#5$2"}, {"id": 163, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2100_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 164, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯！", "name": "宝巫迦"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2100_1#6$1"}, {"id": 165, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 166, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_purifymagic", "volume": 1.0, "channel": "1"}}, {"id": 167, "prop": "bgeffect", "attributes": {"name": "$eb_light", "layer": 1.0}}, {"id": 168, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2100_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 169, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "求你了，“雷之主”，吾等只希望你能把力量借给吾等！", "name": "宝巫迦"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2100_1#8$1"}, {"id": 170, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "1", "fadetime": 0.5}}, {"id": 171, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 172, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 173, "prop": "bgeffect", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 174, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 2.0, "xstrength": 70.0, "ystrength": 70.0, "vibrato": 70.0, "randomness": 95.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 175, "prop": "bgeffect", "attributes": {"name": "$eb_smock", "layer": 1.0}}, {"id": 176, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$MHR_skillroar_normal", "volume": 2.0}}, {"id": 177, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2102_1#1$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 178, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 179, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 180, "prop": "bgeffect", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 181, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2100_1#10$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 182, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唔——", "name": "宝巫迦"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2100_1#10$1"}, {"id": 183, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1049_catap2_1#13$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 184, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "怎么办，梓兰姐？好像不起效啊！", "name": "空爆"}, "figure_art": "avg_1049_catap2_1#13$2"}, {"id": 185, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1048_orchd2_1#10$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 186, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啧，真是个顽强的家伙。", "name": "梓兰"}, "figure_art": "avg_1048_orchd2_1#10$2"}, {"id": 187, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "明明我们已经对它造成了那么多的伤害，它居然毫无怯意，不仅如此，它还愈战愈勇。", "name": "梓兰"}, "figure_art": "avg_1048_orchd2_1#10$2"}, {"id": 188, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1048_orchd2_1#9$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 189, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是“诅咒”剥夺了它的意志吗？", "name": "梓兰"}, "figure_art": "avg_1048_orchd2_1#9$2"}, {"id": 190, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1048_orchd2_1#3$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 191, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "还是说，是它——", "name": "梓兰"}, "figure_art": "avg_1048_orchd2_1#3$2"}, {"id": 192, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1049_catap2_1#7$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 193, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "梓兰姐，不对，“雷之主”的样子——", "name": "空爆"}, "figure_art": "avg_1049_catap2_1#7$2"}, {"id": 194, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 195, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "异变陡生。"}}, {"id": 196, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在挣脱了宝巫迦的力量之后，这一次，“雷之主”并没有立刻袭来，而是开始了痛苦的嘶吼。"}}, {"id": 197, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“雷之主”的身体在不断地挣扎，黑气在它身上如同蒸汽一般冒出，令人毛骨悚然。"}}, {"id": 198, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1049_catap2_1#15$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 199, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "梓兰姐，它的样子，它看起来要被“诅咒”彻底吞噬了！难道我们只能杀死它了吗？", "name": "空爆"}, "figure_art": "avg_1049_catap2_1#15$2"}, {"id": 200, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1048_orchd2_1#8$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 201, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......空爆，不能留手了。", "name": "梓兰"}, "figure_art": "avg_1048_orchd2_1#8$2"}, {"id": 202, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1048_orchd2_1#9$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 203, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果“雷之主”真的被“诅咒”吞噬，一定会酿成大祸。", "name": "梓兰"}, "figure_art": "avg_1048_orchd2_1#9$2"}, {"id": 204, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1049_catap2_1#15$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 205, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......我知道了。", "name": "空爆"}, "figure_art": "avg_1049_catap2_1#15$2"}, {"id": 206, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1048_orchd2_1#6$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 207, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "宝巫迦，明白了吗？", "name": "梓兰"}, "figure_art": "avg_1048_orchd2_1#6$2"}, {"id": 208, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不必考虑任何事，我们已经尽了我们最大的努力，无论得到什么样的结果，我们也只能坦然接受。", "name": "梓兰"}, "figure_art": "avg_1048_orchd2_1#6$2"}, {"id": 209, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2100_1#11$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 210, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......嗯。", "name": "宝巫迦"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2100_1#11$1"}, {"id": 211, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1048_orchd2_1#5$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 212, "prop": "multiline", "attributes": {"name": "梓兰", "content": "趁现在，它还在挣扎，把它——"}}, {"id": 213, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1048_orchd2_1#4$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 214, "prop": "multiline", "attributes": {"name": "梓兰", "content": "咦？"}}, {"id": 215, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 216, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 217, "prop": "bgeffect", "attributes": {"name": "$eb_hyper", "layer": 1.0}}, {"id": 218, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 219, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1049_catap2_1#7$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 220, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "雷光虫？", "name": "空爆"}, "figure_art": "avg_1049_catap2_1#7$2"}, {"id": 221, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2100_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 222, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "什么时候......", "name": "宝巫迦"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2100_1#5$1"}, {"id": 223, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1049_catap2_1#8$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 224, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是从竹林那边飞过来的！", "name": "空爆"}, "figure_art": "avg_1049_catap2_1#8$2"}, {"id": 225, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 226, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "灰暗的地下遗迹之中，不知何时，架起了一道青色的“桥”。"}}, {"id": 227, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而组成这道“桥”的，正是从地下竹林的方向飞来的雷光虫们。"}}, {"id": 228, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "它们越来越多地开始在“雷之主”身边环绕，仿佛正在酝酿着什么。"}}, {"id": 229, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "随着雷光虫的增多，“雷之主”身上的黑气也变得更加旺盛。"}}, {"id": 230, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但是，在那些青色萤火的照耀下，“雷之主”竟也显得少了几分污浊，多了一丝危险的美丽。"}}, {"id": 231, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1048_orchd2_1#4$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 232, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "它们难道是受到了“雷之主”的召唤？但是......为什么？", "name": "梓兰"}, "figure_art": "avg_1048_orchd2_1#4$2"}, {"id": 233, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“雷之主”，难道你——", "name": "梓兰"}, "figure_art": "avg_1048_orchd2_1#4$2"}, {"id": 234, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1049_catap2_1#12$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 235, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "梓兰姐，我有一种直觉。", "name": "空爆"}, "figure_art": "avg_1049_catap2_1#12$2"}, {"id": 236, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "它没有被“诅咒”完全侵染......它一直都在和“诅咒”对抗，并且，现在，它快要赢了？", "name": "空爆"}, "figure_art": "avg_1049_catap2_1#12$2"}, {"id": 237, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 238, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在所有人迟疑之际，“雷之主”的痛苦似乎减弱了几分，它敏捷地跳上了高处。"}}, {"id": 239, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "它站在那里，高昂地抬起了它的头颅，发出一声悠长的吼声。"}}, {"id": 240, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "然后——地裂山崩。"}}, {"id": 241, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 242, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 243, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 244, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 245, "prop": "bgeffect", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 246, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 247, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "71_g2_impermanence_room", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 248, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 249, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 250, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 251, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2107_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 252, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唔——我还能战斗！", "name": "受伤的武士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2107_1#1$1"}, {"id": 253, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2108_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 254, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "别逞强。你的位置有其他武士顶上，现在先好好休息吧！", "name": "泡影国百姓"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2108_1#1$1"}, {"id": 255, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2107_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 256, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我，我杀了好几只野兽！我没有给将军丢人！", "name": "受伤的武士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2107_1#1$1"}, {"id": 257, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2108_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 258, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "放心吧，所有人都是好样的。现在，好好休息吧。", "name": "泡影国百姓"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2108_1#1$1"}, {"id": 259, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（低声）陛下，斑弥罗大人，还有各位，我们会把我们的国家保卫好，请你们一定要平安无事啊......", "name": "泡影国百姓"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2108_1#1$1"}, {"id": 260, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2107_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 261, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "咦......", "name": "受伤的武士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2107_1#1$1"}, {"id": 262, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2108_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 263, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯？", "name": "泡影国百姓"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2108_1#1$1"}, {"id": 264, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2107_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 265, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我是不是眼花了？我怎么看到“御轮”那里，聚集起了乌云？", "name": "受伤的武士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2107_1#1$1"}, {"id": 266, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 267, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "泡影城中，人们共同抬起了头，看向了“御轮”——"}}, {"id": 268, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 269, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 270, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 271, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 272, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 273, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 274, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_black", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 275, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 276, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_thunders_amb", "volume": 1.0, "channel": "2"}}, {"id": 277, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.6, "r": 1.0, "g": 1.0, "b": 1.0, "fadetime": 0.1, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 278, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.03, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 279, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 1.0, "g": 1.0, "b": 1.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 280, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 281, "prop": "bgeffect", "attributes": {"name": "$eb_darkcloud_thunder", "layer": 1.0, "x": 0.0, "xto": 0.0, "y": 140.0, "movetime": 25.0}}, {"id": 282, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 283, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一道粗壮的天雷突破夜晚的乌云，砸在了“御轮”方向的雪山之中。"}}, {"id": 284, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "若是有人离得近一些，他会发现，天雷居然生生地在地上砸出一个大洞，而大洞通往的地方，深不见底。"}}, {"id": 285, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但他一定听得到，那一声从地底传来的震天怒吼——"}}, {"id": 286, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "2", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 287, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 288, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 289, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 290, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 291, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 292, "prop": "bgeffect", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 293, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 294, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 295, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_black", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 296, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$MHR_hyper_insect", "channel": "3", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 297, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.1}}, {"id": 298, "prop": "Effect", "attributes": {"name": "$e_071cg_hyper"}}, {"id": 299, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$MHR_hyper_roar", "channel": "4", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 300, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 301, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$MHR_hyper_roar2", "channel": "5", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 302, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 303, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$MHR_skillroar_hyper", "channel": "6", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 304, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {"image": "71_i09", "screenadapt": "coverall", "fadetime": 0.0}}, {"id": 305, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 306, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 1.5, "xstrength": 70.0, "ystrength": 70.0, "vibrato": 70.0, "randomness": 95.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 307, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$MHR_bat_monsterhunter2boss_intro", "key": "$MHR_bat_monsterhunter2boss_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 308, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 309, "prop": "bgeffect", "attributes": {"name": "$eb_hyper", "layer": 1.0}}, {"id": 310, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那是饱含野性的怒吼。"}}, {"id": 311, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "伴随着怒吼，粗壮的天雷击穿了或许本就没有那么牢固的岩盘，砸在了“雷之主”的身上。"}}, {"id": 312, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "虽然只是刹那间的电光，却让原本灰暗的地下空间都仿佛为之一震。"}}, {"id": 313, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沐浴在雷光之下的“雷之主”，仿佛完成了最后一点蜕变，它再次发出一声怒吼。"}}, {"id": 314, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "这一次，青色的闪电缠满了它的周身。"}}, {"id": 315, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "竖立的鬃毛像纯白的浪涛被骤然定格，每一缕都裹着闪电，电弧在毛尖炸裂，洒下碎星。"}}, {"id": 316, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "鳞甲犹如碧玉，其间流淌着金白光河。尾巴甩动，电火花在空中拉出一条条琥珀色的光鞭，将黑暗划开一道道裂痕。"}}, {"id": 317, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "天雷砸开的洞中，洒下一缕月光。"}}, {"id": 318, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在月光照耀之下，它恍若世间最尊贵的王者。"}}, {"id": 319, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "所有的野兽都在这一刻停下了它们的行动。"}}, {"id": 320, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 321, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 322, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 323, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 324, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 325, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 326, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "71_g12_invertedaltar_dawn", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 327, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 328, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 329, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 330, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1048_orchd2_1#4$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 331, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "它......难道依靠雷电自己清除了诅咒？", "name": "梓兰"}, "figure_art": "avg_1048_orchd2_1#4$2"}, {"id": 332, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1049_catap2_1#7$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 333, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不，梓兰姐，你仔细看。", "name": "空爆"}, "figure_art": "avg_1049_catap2_1#7$2"}, {"id": 334, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "它的身上依然散发着“诅咒”的黑气......但是它的行动，看起来和之前很不一样......", "name": "空爆"}, "figure_art": "avg_1049_catap2_1#7$2"}, {"id": 335, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "它不是清除了“诅咒”，而是克服了“诅咒”，完全把“诅咒”变成了自己力量的一部分！", "name": "空爆"}, "figure_art": "avg_1049_catap2_1#7$2"}, {"id": 336, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1049_catap2_1#1$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 337, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "梓兰姐，看来好像是我们多此一举了。", "name": "空爆"}, "figure_art": "avg_1049_catap2_1#1$2"}, {"id": 338, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1048_orchd2_1#7$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 339, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......是啊，这片大地上的事情真是永远不能一概而论。", "name": "梓兰"}, "figure_art": "avg_1048_orchd2_1#7$2"}, {"id": 340, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1048_orchd2_1#1$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 341, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我们自以为从前代陛下那里得到了关键的情报，以为我们要做的事情是拯救“雷之主”。", "name": "梓兰"}, "figure_art": "avg_1048_orchd2_1#1$2"}, {"id": 342, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我们心心念念地想要拯救“雷之主”，想要将它从“诅咒”的深渊中解放出来......", "name": "梓兰"}, "figure_art": "avg_1048_orchd2_1#1$2"}, {"id": 343, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1048_orchd2_1#2$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 344, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "结果，它看来并不怎么需要我们的拯救。", "name": "梓兰"}, "figure_art": "avg_1048_orchd2_1#2$2"}, {"id": 345, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1049_catap2_1#4$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 346, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "也不一定啦。", "name": "空爆"}, "figure_art": "avg_1049_catap2_1#4$2"}, {"id": 347, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1049_catap2_1#9$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 348, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "野兽总是在战斗中磨练自己，如果没有和我们的战斗，它恐怕也没有办法克服“诅咒”。", "name": "空爆"}, "figure_art": "avg_1049_catap2_1#9$2"}, {"id": 349, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1049_catap2_1#5$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 350, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "从这个角度来说，我们也算是“拯救”了它，不是吗？", "name": "空爆"}, "figure_art": "avg_1049_catap2_1#5$2"}, {"id": 351, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1048_orchd2_1#7$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 352, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......也许吧。", "name": "梓兰"}, "figure_art": "avg_1048_orchd2_1#7$2"}, {"id": 353, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4215_buddyC_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 354, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$MHR_cat_voice1", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 355, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "陛下，趁现在，对它使用御龙术喵！", "name": "政宗"}, "figure_art": "avg_4215_buddyC_1#1$1"}, {"id": 356, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "让它的力量为你所用喵！", "name": "政宗"}, "figure_art": "avg_4215_buddyC_1#1$1"}, {"id": 357, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2100_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 358, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "吾试一试——", "name": "宝巫迦"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2100_1#9$1"}, {"id": 359, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 360, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 361, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一道雷光劈下，直接将宝巫迦手中的翔虫打落，“雷之主”不屑地喷了喷气，似乎并不满意宝巫迦的行为。"}}, {"id": 362, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但它没有进行下一步行动，只是静静地看着宝巫迦。"}}, {"id": 363, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "像是在等待着什么。"}}, {"id": 364, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1049_catap2_1#6$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 365, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "看来，不彻底战胜它，它是不愿意让你对它使用御龙术的。", "name": "空爆"}, "figure_art": "avg_1049_catap2_1#6$2"}, {"id": 366, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2100_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 367, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......是啊。", "name": "宝巫迦"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2100_1#8$1"}, {"id": 368, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 369, "prop": "bgeffect", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 370, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 371, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 372, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 373, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 374, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_black", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 375, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 376, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {"image": "71_i10", "screenadapt": "coverall", "fadetime": 0.0}}, {"id": 377, "prop": "bgeffect", "attributes": {"name": "$eb_hyper", "x": 300.0, "layer": 1.0}}, {"id": 378, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 379, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 380, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在得知真相后，吾是对你心存愧疚的，“雷之主”。", "name": "宝巫迦"}}, {"id": 381, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "毕竟，你只是“诅咒”的受害者，况且，如果不是你凭借本能捕食被“诅咒”的野兽，或许“诅咒”的蔓延会更加迅猛。", "name": "宝巫迦"}}, {"id": 382, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但是，将你招至泡影国的并非吾等，这些年吾的国家和国民也一直生活在你的阴影之下。", "name": "宝巫迦"}}, {"id": 383, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "况且，无论如何，吾最敬爱的母亲还是死在你的手上......", "name": "宝巫迦"}}, {"id": 384, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "吾也不能就这样轻易放下心中的怨怼。", "name": "宝巫迦"}}, {"id": 385, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$MHR_normalroar3", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 386, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（低吼）", "name": "“雷之主”"}}, {"id": 387, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "它听不懂你说的这些的，宝巫迦。", "name": "梓兰"}}, {"id": 388, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "它只是野兽，它既不会因为被“御轮”传送到一个奇特的国度就对自己的境遇产生迷茫，也不会因为被“诅咒”侵扰而痛恨自己的命运。", "name": "梓兰"}}, {"id": 389, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "它只是凭借着自己的本性去扛起了这一切。", "name": "梓兰"}}, {"id": 390, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "来到了新的天地，那就在新的天地活下去。", "name": "梓兰"}}, {"id": 391, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "被“诅咒”侵扰，那就克服“诅咒”。", "name": "梓兰"}}, {"id": 392, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "咒鬼要杀它，它就杀死咒鬼。", "name": "梓兰"}}, {"id": 393, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "除此之外，它不关心你是否恨它，也不关心你是否爱它，这对它来说，并不重要......", "name": "梓兰"}}, {"id": 394, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "生命的本能，就只是活下去。", "name": "梓兰"}}, {"id": 395, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "没错，即使还有“御轮”这个威胁当前，它还是不愿意和我们联手。", "name": "空爆"}}, {"id": 396, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "毕竟，我们要做的事情，可是在挑战它作为王者的威严。", "name": "空爆"}}, {"id": 397, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "说到底，最后还是要交给手中的武器嘛。", "name": "空爆"}}, {"id": 398, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......说得也是。", "name": "宝巫迦"}}, {"id": 399, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "旭日东升，今天是个狩猎的好日子。"}}, {"id": 400, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 401, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 402, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 403, "prop": "bgeffect", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 404, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 405, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 406, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}], "OPTIONTRACE": true}